description: Expansion of series related to Liouville's Last Theorem: g.f. sum_{t>0} (-1)^(t+1) *x^(t*(t+1)/2) / ( (1-x^t)^3 *product_{i=1..t} (1-x^i) ).
links: G. E. Andrews, Some debts I owe, Seminaire Lotharingien Combinatoire, Paper B42a, Issue 42, 2000; see (7.4).
author: _N. J. A. Sloane_, Feb 24 2001
